# {{medicine}} Cylindrical instrument for introducing an object into a tubular anatomical structure, or for dilating such a structure, as with an esophageal bougie.
==French==
===Etymology===
Named from [[Bougie]], the French name for the Algerian town of [[w:Béjaïa|Béjaïa]] (Arabic {{ARchar|[[بجاية]]}}), formerly known for exporting candles.

